title: Best place for your wedding
body: Looking for a place to stay in Negombo? Then look no further than Avenra Garden Hotel, a luxury small hotel that brings the best of Negombo to your doorstep. Rooms at Avenra Garden Hotel provide air conditioning, and guests can stay connected with free wifi. In addition, while staying at Avenra Garden Hotel guests have access to room service. You can also enjoy a pool and free breakfast. Need a place to park? Free parking is available at Avenra Garden Hotel. For those interested in checking out popular landmarks while visiting Negombo, Avenra Garden Hotel is located a short distance from Angurukaramulla Temple (0.5 mi) and Abhayasekararama Temple (0.5 mi). If you’re looking for a Chinese restaurant, consider a visit to Kreeptow Lounge & Restaurant, Sea Joy Restaurant, or Seafood Club, which are all conveniently located a short distance from Avenra Garden Hotel. We’re sure you’ll enjoy your stay at Avenra Garden Hotel as you experience everything Negombo has to offer.

title: Top place for your event in Ruwanpura
body: Hotel located between Ratnapura and Pelmadulla. Easy access and parking available. Quiet surroundings. Washrooms in better quality. Had Lunch, Buffet around 2:30 PM. Excellent taste and quality. 540 LKR per person as at May 2015. Good price for quality food. Cakes and Pastries are also available
